*Rok* je bio veoma kratak (The time period was very short).
On je čekao *rok* da bi dobio rezultate (He waited for a time period to get the results).
U tom *roku*, oni su uspeli da obave posao (In that time period, they managed to finish the job).
Ugovor je imao *rok* od tri meseca (The contract had a time period of three months).
Većina studenata je završila projekat u zadatom *roku* (Most of the students completed the project within the given time period).